{"tid":766820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃錦星否認「四電一腦」扼殺收買佬，而是想整治「山寨式」不環保回收手法。","createTime":"2018-08-04T03:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T07:23:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1db0fc6e36dbc9e5e22f3970214ff9ebf9cbdeb5","tid":766820,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1282716/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1282716%2F&d=OyPra5W0UsMmW4Xh8JxRCG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ea0ff7c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1282716%2F&h=4874ca39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1282716/</a><br />\n<br />\n環境局局長黃錦星指，實施「四電一腦」廢電器電子產品生產者責任計畫，並非要扼殺「收買佬」行業，而是要整治「山寨式」和「粗獷式」的不環保回收手法。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180804/_2018080410012649842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180804%2F_2018080410012649842.jpg&h=80a3113a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">黃錦星霸氣回應市民對「四電一腦」的誤解，他指若以不環保方式拆解舊電器會毒害環境，同時危及回收工人健康。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n黃錦星明白有聲音認為新政策或扼殺小型回收商的生存空間，但他指出，若有「收賣佬」以「山寨式」和「粗獷式」的不環保方式拆解舊電器，不但毒害環境，還同時危及回收工人的健康。"},{"pid":"d09e65bed85bd92fdddc680747572892722f0814","tid":766820,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"黃錦星又指，「四電一腦」的除舊服務去年已實施先行計畫，運作大致順暢。他重申持牌回收商有服務承諾，市民只要及早預約，可做到同日回收舊電器及安裝新電器。<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，零售商有責任告知消費者享有免費除舊服務，提醒市民若有店鋪因為提供除舊服務而收取額外費用，有關說法或不符法例，涉及誤導，可向當局舉報。"},{"pid":"32c928008bd7cd11dd4ba4328ab0edfaaa57dd7b","tid":766820,"uid":132587,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"呢個山寨政府養咁多無腦垃圾仲唔環保啦 <br />\n個閪腦諗埋曬咁多離地橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a1bb48a4a0acbeae26ffe6c1cb36aa1090e1b5","tid":766820,"uid":18465,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣危及緊回收工人全家呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb7306ce9498920cde3234f993f79b5372eea30","tid":766820,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:13:17.000Z","msg":"佢自己換部冷氣雪櫃試下先啦，on9"},{"pid":"f8bffb6ad6c33179ff37264e7243b08b4ad5359d","tid":766820,"uid":119330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"佢個腦係咪裝左屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad2c64488e950913a27d8104e4e09b522a64fcf","tid":766820,"uid":56462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<br />\n垃圾政策<br />\n換個電器都咁撚煩"},{"pid":"fe0d09e9b5f0d44dac2092f32129e2c134dd3cf9","tid":766820,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e65db3b5bedb5c9b18314b6542899e6caae7af","tid":766820,"uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"膠袋稅已經on9<br />\n收埋d錢唔係去攪環保<br />\n係比d商戶袋入自己袋<br />\n<br />\n遲d收垃圾費<br />\n垃圾唔駛分類<br />\n根本就係借題收水<br />\n跟攪環保無關"},{"pid":"a0d9b81fdb813b8848ac727b6b01e622953db1ee","tid":766820,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"Z&gt;B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002acab99be5006fd34a95a414a9982fdf83b1e3","tid":766820,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1db0fc6e36dbc9e5e22f3970214ff9ebf9cbdeb5","tid":766820,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1282716/\" data-s